jQuery.ImageHoverGrow animation plugin
===================================================

What is ImageHoverGrow
-----------------
ImageHoverGrow is a jQuery 1.7 plugin which displays the image in actual size when hovering over downscaled image. See the example-page to see it in action.

License
-----------------
MIT
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
name: jQuery.Image.HoverGrow
tagline: On hover event, shows a floating image with natural dimensions.
